headline: 5 Insightful Analyst Questions From NetApp’s Q3 Earnings Call
summary: NetApp’s third quarter results were met with a positive market reaction, reflecting management’s focus on high-margin segments and operational efficiency. CEO George Kurian pointed to the company’s unified data platform and strong momentum in all-flash arrays and public cloud services as key contributors. He also highlighted that AI-driven infrastructure deals nearly doubled year over year, and that recent product launches—such as AFX and the AI Data Engine—helped address growing customer demand
